	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Gratia filii dei tecum.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ne mirere, doctissime Bullingere, meum diuturnum silentium, ne dicam, quod te non reddiderim certiorem, an is quem tuis literis domine commendaras, posset abeunti succedere <persName type="auto_name">Voglero</persName>.<note type="margin">a.R.: <persName type="auto_name">Joh.Vogler</persName> von 1562–67 Schaffner in <placeName ref="l405" cert="high">Rappoltsweiler</placeName></note></s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">At <persName ref="p20051" cert="high">Vertumnus</persName><note xml:id="fn1" type="footnote" n="1">Gott des steten Wandels; vgl. <bibl>Adagia</bibl>, 2, 2, 74 (<bibl>LB</bibl> II 473).</note> ille noster ex uno ore calidum et frigidum spirans responsum distulit, neque Voglerus suum abdicabit munus, tametsi dicat se sub autumno paraturum discessum.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Hodie tibi scripturus rursum scripsi domine; sed ex inserta schedula intelliges negotium; ita arridet illi lucellum etc.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ecclesiola nostra lente festinat.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l411" cert="high">Richenvillę</placeName> regnant ubiquiste magna ecclesię iactura<note xml:id="fna" type="footnote" n="a">a.R.: nach Erbs Vertreibung 1560/61</note>.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Legisti, opinor, <persName type="auto_name">Palatinorum</persName> responsa in <placeName type="auto_name">Farczbachium</placeName><note xml:id="fnb" type="footnote" n="b">a.R.: =Marbach?</note> (ut vocant).</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Non cessat Stentor pro rostris ad raucim / ranzim usque clamare; sed maior pars <placeName type="auto_name">Argentorat[ensium]</placeName> nauseant eius calumnias.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Magistratus caute agens metuit, ne turba excitetur.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Conventus principum in ianuario futurus est; quid decernent, dies declarabit.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ingens spes <placeName type="auto_name">Selestad</placeName>, <placeName ref="l101" cert="high">Colmariensem</placeName> et reliquas civitates decem, quę domui Austriacę obpignoratę sunt, Christum recepturas.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Haganoa, quae primaria est, exactis sacrificis concionatorem substituerunt quam sequentur et [...] <placeName type="auto_name">Obernehenen</placeName>, <placeName type="auto_name">Colmarię</placeName> totus senatus conspirarunt in Christum, excepto uno et altero.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Oramus strenue ut Christi regnum propagetur.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Et vos orate pro nobis.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Raptim die sali [...] anno Christi natalitium 1565.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuus <persName ref="p1010" cert="high">Matthias Erbius</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Incomparabili viro pietate ac eruditione d. Henricho Bullingero, ecclesię <placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name">Tigurinę</placeName> theologo atque antistiti fidelissimo, suo fratri.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
